{"tid":983610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 輪胎充氣爆炸　工人遭氣流擊傷頭送院","createTime":"2019-01-16T06:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T10:03:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"41ae687f25036a9120a206805695605f925066ae","tid":983610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"將軍澳環保大道發生工業意外，今早(16日)9時12分，一名61歲姓陳工人在堆填區內的土木工程拓展署地盤，為一輛泥頭車的輪胎充氣時，輪胎突然爆炸，產生強大氣流，陳首當其衝，被擊中頭部「暈一暈」，眼部亦受傷，在場工友見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n消防及救護員接報趕至，為傷者急救後，恢復知覺送院，警方調查後，列作有人意外受傷-工業意外跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190116/bkn-20190116100423567-0116_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190116%2Fbkn-20190116100423567-0116_00822_001.html&d=ll1HIowsE26aSNlWinny4xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f742e2be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190116/bkn-20190116100423567-0116_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e9158decb4362f975d997c1087e5ae2b5ca12705","tid":983610,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LKdkeR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LKdkeR.gif&h=398160e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47fbb5a4c259d118e744670af2ef71429cc46da7","tid":983610,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pFkNJH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pFkNJH.gif&h=34f10773&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a82c56a60d59c9c9382ec6be67f4c273e7e00dfc","tid":983610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2Ya9Z8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2Ya9Z8.gif&h=92c578c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c58472293d0def79d3863fe938812dd67c91569a","t